{% extends "layout.njk" %}
{% set activePage = 'about' %}
{% block pageTitle %} Yoku Sushi | About {% endblock %}

{% block content %}
	<div class='about'>
		<p>Welcome to Yoku Sushi!</p>

		<p>
			Here in Yoku Sushi, our motto is "Eat Well, Eat Healthy". We bring to you fresh and nutritious meals, offering you an authentic modern Japanese dining experience. 
		</p>
		<p>
			We cater for both eat-in diners as well as takeaway. 
		</p>
		<p>
			As with Japanese style dining, all dishes on your order are brought out as they come hot and piping straight from the kitchen. If you prefer them to be served in courses, please let us know. 
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>Food Allergy Notice:</strong>
			Please be advised that food prepared here may contain these ingredients:
			Cereals containing gluten, curstaceans, egg, fish, milk, molluscs, mustard, sesame seeds, soya & sulphur dioxide.
		</p>
		<p>
			If you have any allergies and special requests, please make an enquiry and we will try our best to accommodate your needs.
		</p>
	</div>

{% endblock %}
